    "bg field: 'transparent' (alpha-keys the baked checker) or { r,g,b,tolerance }.",
    "watermark: corner box (in source pixels) to alpha-erase. Default = 12% pct.",
    "Add new entries at the top of `entries` as new sheets land.",
